VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.Exec\s*\(\s*["'][^"']*["']\s*\+|\.Exec\s*\(\s*fmt\.Sprintf\s*\(["'][^"']*%[sv]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:\.Exec\s*\(\s*"[^"]*\?|\.Exec\s*\(\s*"[^"]*@|PreparedStatement|parameterized
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects GORM Exec() calls executing dynamically built SQL strings.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Exec() with Unparameterized SQL.
